CREATED:20240603T162450Z
DESCRIPTION:Open community bicycle repair event at the <a href="https://oak
 citycares.org/" target="_blank">Oak City Cares Multiservices Center</a>\, <
 span>a hub for connecting individuals and families at risk of\, or currentl
 y experiencing\, houselessness.</span> We host a repair event at OCC every 
 2nd Saturday of the month from 1-3pm. We fix/replace brakes\, clean chains/
 drivetrains\, tune shifters\, fix flats\, and make other minor adjustments.
  We also distribute refurbished bikes on a first-come\, first-served basis.
 <br> <br><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VJGkxpowGLi9LNfFj
 neI8mNoEKFTLBa6J27K8PHTpyE/edit?usp=sharing" class="pastedDriveLink-3">RCK 
 Volunteer Signup</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250807T115621Z
LOCATION:Oak City Cares 1430 S. Wilmington Street\, Raleigh\, NC 27603
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bike Repair & Distribution @ Oak City Cares
TRANSP:OPAQUE
