UID:3t5df4qtjm2g2hj1el6mlj8d89@google.com
CREATED:20190904T205052Z
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh Community Kickstand will be repairing 20 used bicycles\
 , making them ready to be placed with people in the homeless and at-risk co
 mmunity.\n\nWe are looking for volunteers of all skill levels.\n\nWe will p
 rovide bikes\, parts\, bike stands\, some tools\, and some knowledge. If yo
 u have your own tools\, feel free to bring your own hand tools.\n\nThis is 
 a great opportunity for anyone who would like to learn how to repair their 
 own bikes\, as we will be performing a wide range of repairs and you can le
 arn from many of our talented volunteers.\n\nPlease do not bring bicycles t
 o donate at this event\, as we will have very limited ability to transport 
 bikes from this event.
LAST-MODIFIED:20190904T205052Z
LOCATION:Humble Pie Parking Lot\, 311 S Harrington St\, Raleigh\, NC 27601
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bike Repair Clinic @ SparkCon
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
