DESCRIPTION:Cranksgiving is a fun choose-your-own-adventure event all about
  riding a bike and helping folks in our community during the holiday season
 .\n\nYou’ll get a list of essential food items\, some bonus challenges\, an
 d a map of nearby grocery stores. You can also help by picking up and deliv
 ering goods that others have donated at our drop-off points.\n\nHowever you
  choose to participate is entirely up to you. Every one can make a differen
 ce\, whether you’re buying\, carrying\, or collecting!\n\nWe will be giving
  out points for weight\, distance\, and key items. So grab your cargo bike\
 , panniers\, backpack\, and any and everything you can mount to your bike t
 o carry a load.\n \nRegistration: 1:00pm\nStart: 1:30pm\nCut-Off: 3:30pm
