DTSTAMP:20260401T152747Z
UID:4n95vsjunphfpjjl3sshlefqqo@google.com
CREATED:20180208T004930Z
DESCRIPTION:\nLearn bicycle maintenance skills\, help out some people in ne
 ed and drink some great beer. \n\nWe will be fixing some donated bikes\, ma
 king them ready to be placed with folks in need in Raleigh. Since May we ha
 ve placed 3 dozen bikes with people who need them for basic transportation.
 \n\nNo skills needed. We will have experienced people there to work with an
 d learn from.\n\nWe will have some bike stands and tools\, but if your own 
 tools you may want to bring them.\n\nWe can really use lights and locks. Li
 ghts are required by law. Locks are a necessity. Most of the people we plac
 e bikes with live in a shelter or in encampments around the city so without
  a lock any bike we give them gets gone in a hurry.  \n\nhttps://www.facebo
 ok.com/events/299158993943717/
