UID:17vakgchc0o7utargclrevpu4k@google.com
CREATED:20250617T113104Z
DESCRIPTION:\nJoin us for an alleycat & cookout! New to alleycats? Alleycat
 s are fun\, choose-your-own-adventure rides inspired by bike couriers. You’
 ll get a list of stops\, plan a route\, and hit as many stops as you can (o
 r want to) before the cutoff. Each stop earns you a random crayon. At the e
 nd\, use them to color in a drawing. Best ones win prizes!\n\nRide solo or 
 party-pace with a group. Perfect for beginners\, newcomers\, veteran townie
 s\, and everyone in between. Featuring a post-ride cookout with hot dogs (v
 eggie and meet)\, drinks\, and snacks. Proceeds go to Raleigh Community Kic
 kstand\, a collective providing free repairs\, bikes\, and training for fol
 ks in need. See you there!\n \n\nMelted Crayon Alleycat & Cookout - A party
 -pace\, choose-your-own-adventure ride with a coloring twist benefitting Ra
 leigh Community Kickstand!\n$10 Suggested Donation\nWhere: Jaycee Park | 24
 05 Wade Ave\nWhen: Saturday\, July 12 | Registration: 5pm | Start: 6pm | Cu
 toff + Cookout: 8pm\nFree safety checks at registration. Cookout + coloring
  contest after cutoff.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250628T115412Z
LOCATION:Jaycee Park\, 2405 Wade Ave\, Raleigh\, NC 27607\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Melted Crayon Alleycat & Cookout
TRANSP:OPAQUE
